title: 6 WEEKS FREE + 3 MONTHS FREE PARKING! Gorgeous 1BR in Mill District!
posting_body: ['OX-OP is a brand new boutique apartment community in the heart of Minneapolis’ Mill District neighborhood!', 'OX-OP is conveniently located steps from the Grand Rounds bike trail, green & blue Metro Transit light rail lines, multiple parks, and a plethora of entertainment and dining options.', 'It was designed to seamlessly meld with the neighborhood, elevating a sustainable, modern aesthetic while paying homage to the brick flour mills that have long occupied the area.', 'Our community features multiple state-of-the-art amenities including a stunning rooftop deck, cedar sauna, herb garden, and upgraded unit interiors for your everyday life.', '#512 --', 'Plan T', '#512 is finished with vinyl oak plank flooring and white quartz countertops.', 'This unit also features ample storage, Downtown views, and a smart, functional walk-through design.', '*Photos of a similar unit*', 'For more info and to apply: <URL>', 'Online pricing is reflective of 6 week free special!', 'Minneapolis -- Mpls -- Mill District -- Downtown East -- East Town -- Downtown -- U of M -- Boutique -- Luxury -- Scandinavian -- Mid-Century Modern -- Bike Friendly -- Pet, Dog, Cat Friendly -- Green Living -- Sustainable -- Electric Car Charging -- New Construction -- Leased by Solhem']
